                    Gara Sǝllāse for 7 birr </desc>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="a5">
                  <desc> Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</foreign>, is
